<item>
            <title>[LU-13609] lctl --device MGS llog_catlist doesn&apos;t list all config files.</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13609</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When trying to do a catlist it&#160; is limited to ~304.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
nbp8-mds1 ~ # debugfs -c /dev/mapper/nbp8--vg-mgs8 -R &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;ls -l /CONFIGS/&apos;&lt;/span&gt;   | wc -l
debugfs 1.45.2.wc1 (27-May-2019)
/dev/mapper/nbp8--vg-mgs8: catastrophic mode - not reading inode or group bitmaps
330
nbp8-mds1 ~ # lctl --device MGS llog_catlist |wc -l 
305
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
nbp2-mds ~ # debugfs -c /dev/mapper/nbp2--vg-mgs2 -R &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;ls -l /CONFIGS/&apos;&lt;/span&gt;   | wc -l
debugfs 1.45.2.wc1 (27-May-2019)
/dev/mapper/nbp2--vg-mgs2: catastrophic mode - not reading inode or group bitmaps
353
nbp2-mds ~ # lctl --device MGS llog_catlist |wc -l 
304
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
